(secondQuint)Clinical Evaluation of the IONA Test for Non-invasive Pre Natal Screening in Twin Pregnancies.

 350 low risk and 150 high risk women with twin pregnancies will be recruited to produce a large cohort evaluation the use of the IONA test in twin pregnancies for Downs, Edwards and Patau syndrome.

 Reserve samples will also be used to further develop the test for other chromosomal abnormalities.

